Netizens submitted that Nanjing Medical University and Jiangsu Provincial People's Hospital refused to give in and continued to work today.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
Yesterday (December 12 evening), students (mostly postgraduates) protested in the North Building of the Outpatient Department of the First Affiliated Hospital of Kunming Medical University, demanding equal pay for equal work and leaving school to return home.
A conflict occurred at the scene, and several teachers controlled a graduate student and snatched his mobile phone.
As of now, the matter has not been resolved, and the school and hospital have not given a response
